              <section>

                  
          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>January is a quiet month on the 2026 gaming calendar, but this frees you up to check out games that flew under your radar. If you're looking for something to fill the quiet period on PC, Fanatical is offering three new bundle deals worth checking out. The new <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Save+On+Dozens+Of+PC+Games+With+These+New+Year+Bundle+Deals&amp;fnauthor=darranged&amp;fndate=2026-01-12+16%3A54%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2026-01-12+16%3A54%3A58&amp;fnarticle_id=6537234&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kqzyfj.com%2Fclick-100770772-13797872%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.fanatical.com%2Fen%2Fpick-and-mix%2Fplatinum-collection-build-your-own-bundle&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Ffanatical-new-year-game-bundles-january-2026%2F1100-6537234%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">January 2026 Platinum Collection</a>, <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Save+On+Dozens+Of+PC+Games+With+These+New+Year+Bundle+Deals&amp;fnauthor=darranged&amp;fndate=2026-01-12+16%3A54%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2026-01-12+16%3A54%3A58&amp;fnarticle_id=6537234&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jdoqocy.com%2Fclick-100770772-13797872%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.fanatical.com%2Fen%2Fpick-and-mix%2Fbuild-your-own-new-year-bundle&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Ffanatical-new-year-game-bundles-january-2026%2F1100-6537234%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">New Year 2026 Collection</a>, and <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Save+On+Dozens+Of+PC+Games+With+These+New+Year+Bundle+Deals&amp;fnauthor=darranged&amp;fndate=2026-01-12+16%3A54%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2026-01-12+16%3A54%3A58&amp;fnarticle_id=6537234&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tkqlhce.com%2Fclick-100770772-13797872%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.fanatical.com%2Fen%2Fpick-and-mix%2Fbuild-your-own-triple-pack&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Ffanatical-new-year-game-bundles-january-2026%2F1100-6537234%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Triple Pack</a> deals are all build-your-own bundle offers that let you mix and match from their own unique lists of games--and the more you add to your bundles, the more you'll save. Each game key can be redeemed on your Steam account, and most are Steam Deck Verified. We've outlined all three bundle deals below, including full lists of all the games you can pick for each.</p><h2>Platinum Collection - Build your own Bundle (January 2026)</h2><figure data-align="center" data-size="large" data-img-src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1701/17013431/4634183-plat26.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4634183" data-ratio="0.5625" data-width="1280" data-embed-type="image"><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1701/17013431/4634183-plat26.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4634183"></a><figcaption>Fanatical's Platinum Collection - Build your own Bundle (January 2026)</figcaption><img src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1701/17013431/4634183-plat26.jpg"></figure><p>Fanatical offers a new selection of curated games every month with the Platinum Collection, and the first bundle of 2026 has some terrific picks. <strong>Buy three or more games to get each one for $3.33, five or more for $3 each, and seven or more for $2.85 each. </strong>Some of our top picks here include the delightfully weird roguelite heist game Turnip Boy Robs a Bank, sci-fi crafting game Next Space Rebels, and you can embrace your inner John Wick with the fast-paced top-down shooter Phantom Squad.</p><p>If nothing grabs your eye here, you can also check out the <a href="https://clicks.trx-hub.com/xid/fandom_32094_gamespot?fntitle=Save+On+Dozens+Of+PC+Games+With+These+New+Year+Bundle+Deals&amp;fnauthor=darranged&amp;fndate=2026-01-12+16%3A54%3A00&amp;fnupdated=2026-01-12+16%3A54%3A58&amp;fnarticle_id=6537234&amp;fntype1=Games&amp;fntype2=News&amp;fntype3=Deals&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tkqlhce.com%2Fclick-100770772-13797872%3Fsid%3Dsubid_value%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.fanatical.com%2Fen%2Fpick-and-mix%2Fbest-of-platinum-collection-build-your-own-bundle&amp;p=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamespot.com%2Farticles%2Ffanatical-new-year-game-bundles-january-2026%2F1100-6537234%2F%3Fftag%3DCAD-01-10abi2f&amp;event_type=click" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">December 2025 Best Of Platinum Collection</a>. It's still active for a few more weeks, and it includes popular games like RoboCop: Rogue City, Fallout 76, and Paradise Killer.</p><ul><li>Agatha Christie: Murder on the Orient Express</li><li>Asterigos: Curse of the Stars</li><li>Dino Path Trail</li><li>Dodgeball Academia</li><li>Duckside</li><li>Fae Tactics</li><li>Grandma, No!</li><li>Grapple Dogs: Cosmic Canines &amp; Grapple Dog Double Pack</li><li>Havendock Complete Edition</li><li>House Builder - The Atomic Age Bundle</li><li>Let's School</li><li>Lil' Guardsman</li><li>MainFrames</li><li>Mika and The Witch's Mountain</li><li>Next Space Rebels</li><li>Painted In Blood</li><li>Phantom Squad</li><li>Ring of Pain</li><li>Train Valley World</li><li>Turnip Boy Robs a Bank</li><li>Windjammers 2</li></ul><hr><h2>Build your own New Year Bundle (2026)</h2><figure data-align="center" data-size="large" data-img-src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1701/17013431/4634186-newyr.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4634186" data-ratio="0.5625" data-width="1280" data-embed-type="image"><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1701/17013431/4634186-newyr.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4634186"></a><figcaption>Fanatical's Build your own New Year Bundle (2026)</figcaption><img src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1701/17013431/4634186-newyr.jpg"></figure><p>Another bundle to help you start 2026 on the right foot, the Build Your Own New Year Bundle offers a curated selection of games for less than $2 each. <strong>Buy three or more games to get each one for $1.65, five or more for $1.60 each, and seven or more for $1.45 each. </strong>Kart-racing fans can grab Dreamworks and Nickelodeon games that see popular characters from film and TV head to the racetrack, Terraformers is an expansive colony builder and resource-management game with roguelike elements, and Tombstar is a top-down sci-fi and western-themed shooter set at the edge of the galaxy.</p><ul><li dir="ltr">Accident</li><li dir="ltr">Afterimage Deluxe Edition</li><li dir="ltr">Airship: Kingdoms Adrift</li><li dir="ltr">Block Factory</li><li dir="ltr">Bzzzt</li><li dir="ltr">Cobra Kai: The Karate Kid Saga Continues</li><li dir="ltr">Din's Legacy</li><li dir="ltr">DreamWorks All-Star Kart Racing</li><li dir="ltr">DunHero</li><li dir="ltr">Echoes of the Plum Grove</li><li dir="ltr">Evoland Legendary Edition</li><li dir="ltr">Golden Chambers</li><li dir="ltr">Hello Goodboy: Deluxe Edition</li><li dir="ltr">Moonlight Pulse</li><li dir="ltr">New Star GP</li><li dir="ltr">Nickelodeon Kart Racers 3: Slime Speedway</li><li dir="ltr">Nova Lands</li><li dir="ltr">Tails of Trainspot</li><li dir="ltr">Terraformers</li><li dir="ltr">The Black Grimoire: Cursebreaker</li><li dir="ltr">TombStar</li><li dir="ltr">Xmas Apocalypse</li><li dir="ltr">Zombasite</li></ul><hr><h2>Build your own Triple Pack (New Year 2026)</h2><figure data-align="center" data-size="large" data-img-src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1701/17013431/4634187-triple.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4634187" data-ratio="0.5625" data-width="1280" data-embed-type="image"><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1701/17013431/4634187-triple.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4634187"></a><figcaption>Build your own Triple Pack (New Year 2026)</figcaption><img src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1701/17013431/4634187-triple.jpg"></figure><p>Another popular bundle deal at Fanatical, the Build Your Own Triple Pack offers a solid selection of titles across myriad genres. <strong>Buy three or more games to get each one for $1, five or more for 95 cents each, and seven or more for 90 cents each.</strong> Some of the great games here include the pixel-fueled RPG Wolfhaven, the devilish style of the fast-paced first-person shooter Hyper Demon, and Everholm is an open-ended RPG that will appeal to fans of minimalist design.</p><ul><li dir="ltr">Ad Infinitum</li><li dir="ltr">Death in Unison</li><li dir="ltr">Depths of Peril</li><li dir="ltr">Din's Curse</li><li dir="ltr">Everholm</li><li dir="ltr">Figment 2: Creed Valley</li><li dir="ltr">For The King - Deluxe Edition</li><li dir="ltr">Hyper Demon</li><li dir="ltr">Knock'Em Out</li><li dir="ltr">Lysfanga: The Time Shift Warrior</li><li dir="ltr">Mercury Fallen</li><li dir="ltr">Nanotale - Typing Chronicles</li><li dir="ltr">One Lonely Outpost</li><li dir="ltr">Polylithic</li><li dir="ltr">The Falconeer: Revolution Remaster</li><li dir="ltr">The Signifier: Director's Cut</li><li dir="ltr">Windward</li><li dir="ltr">Wolfstride</li></ul><p><em>Disclosure: GameSpot and Fanatical are both owned by Fandom.</em></p><div data-embed-type="pinbox" data-ref-id="4304">  <ul>                              <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/lego-icons-lord-of-the-rings-balrog-book-nook-building-set-best-deal/1100-6537313/">Lego Lord Of The Rings Book Nook Gets First Discount At Amazon</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/arrow-video-4k-blu-ray-movies-50-percent-off-at-amazon/1100-6537233/">Save 50% On New Limited-Edition 4K Blu-Rays At Amazon</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/amazon-4k-blu-ray-sale-january-2026-3-for-33-new-movie-deal/1100-6537208/">Recently Released 4K Blu-Rays Are 3 For $33 At Amazon</a></li>                          <li>         <span>+ Show More More Gaming, Tech, and Entertainment Deals &amp; Preorders Links (5)</span>       </li>          <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/teenage-mutant-ninja-turtles-magic-the-gathering-set-preorder-restock-guide/1100-6535373/">TMNT Magic: The Gathering Booster Box Preorders Steeply Discounted</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/lego-sonic-the-hedgehog-building-sets-crossworlds-cars/1100-6536549/">Budget-Friendly Sonic Racing: CrossWorlds Lego Sets Are Available Now</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/lego-harry-potter-sorcerers-stone-25th-anniversary-series-collectors-edition/1100-6537154/">Lego Harry Potter 25th Anniversary Sets Have Arrived, Including A New Collector's Edition</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/lego-star-wars-bb-8-astromech-droid-75452-new-release-2026/1100-6537153/">New Lego Star Wars BB-8 Droid Building Set Is Available Now</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/microsd-express-cards-nintendo-switch-2-best-deals-available-now/1100-6530578/">Double Nintendo Switch 2 Console Storage For Only $33 With Samsung MicroSD Express Deal</a></li>   </ul> </div>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
