</h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0FCJFY734?tag=gamespot-promos-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/dp\/B0FCJFY734?tag=gamespot-promos-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0FCJFY734?tag=gamespot-promos-20">$73 (was $90)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <div><p>Ninja Gaiden 4 Deluxe Edition is also seeing a slight discount at both Amazon and Best Buy, as it's now priced at $73 (was $90). You'll get the base game plus the following extras:</p><ul><li>Future Gameplay Content: "The Two Masters"</li><li>Traditional Dark Blue Ryu Skin</li><li>Legendary Black Falcon Ryu Skin</li><li>Divine Chimera Yakumo Skin</li><li>Raven Master Yakumo Skin</li><li>Divine Chimera Yakumo Weapon Set</li><li>50,000 Bonus NinjaCoin</li><li>Additional In-Game Items:  <ul><li>Life Elixir (x5)</li><li>Divine Life Elixir (x3)</li><li>Incense of Rebirth (x1)</li><li>Crimson Blood Pellets (x2)</li><li>Senjin War Brew (x2)</li><li>Kongou Iron Brew (x2)</li></ul></li></ul></div>                      </div>   </div><p>Our <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/ninja-gaiden-4-review-master-ninja/1900-6418426/" data-ref-id="1900-6418426">Ninja Gaiden 4 review</a> gave it an impressive 8/10, highlighting its incredible combat and brutal boss fights. "Even after barreling through the campaign in a couple of days, I still couldn't stop myself from going back for more," wrote critic Richard Wakeling. "Ninja Gaiden 4 is a brutal menagerie of excessive blood spray, gratifying weapons, and gloriously stylish action. It banishes the sour memories of Ninja Gaiden 3 and has me pining for more character-action games, serving as a wistful reminder that games like Ninja Gaiden, Devil May Cry, and Bayonetta ruled the roost before the recent proliferation of Souls-likes."</p><p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/NINJA-GAIDEN-Ragebound-Playstation-5/dp/B0FD4NMM41?tag=gamespot-promos-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Ninja Gaiden Ragebound</a> on PS5 is down to its lowest price ever at Amazon, now available for $31.12 (was $40). The 2D game features gorgeous pixel art, and it comes with a soundtrack and booklet containing additional details about the game. Since you're essentially saving $30 with the Ninja Gaiden 4 deal, consider using that saved cash to snag another excellent adventure--our <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/ninja-gaiden-ragebound-review-a-cut-above/1900-6418392/" data-ref-id="1900-6418392">review</a> once again awarded it an 8/10.</p><div data-embed-type="pinbox" data-ref-id="4304">  <ul>                              <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/lego-icons-lord-of-the-rings-balrog-book-nook-building-set-best-deal/1100-6537313/">Lego Lord Of The Rings Book Nook Gets First Discount At Amazon</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/arrow-video-4k-blu-ray-movies-50-percent-off-at-amazon/1100-6537233/">Save 50% On New Limited-Edition 4K Blu-Rays At Amazon</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/amazon-4k-blu-ray-sale-january-2026-3-for-33-new-movie-deal/1100-6537208/">Recently Released 4K Blu-Rays Are 3 For $33 At Amazon</a></li>                          <li>         <span>+ Show More More Gaming, Tech, and Entertainment Deals &amp; Preorders L